Date 29th-30th-31st July 2016

Tickets now on sale http://www.Dubsatthebeach.co.uk

Well Guys Great News after a Visit this week we have now Booked the Sea Front again for 450 VDubs on the Sunday and own Camping Field for chilled weekend Live Bands Both Nights -Trade stalls -Food Caters - Bar - toilets-Showers

Limited number of 350 camping plots and 100 passes just to park @ the Beach

Any info Give me a bell 07817971589 Dave

Website now live with Tickets on sale

Adult Weekend will be £25.00 and £5.00 for your Vehicle pass if we don't selling out Adult tickets will be £35.00 on the Gate
Kids Under 16 Free
Dogs -- Free

Saturday Adult Day Visitor @ the Campsite £5.00 Kids Free also Dogs
Sunday Park @ the Beach £5.00 per Car ------if you have paid for Camping then this will be Free

@ the Camping site there will be Free Auto Jumble with trade plot stating from £50.00
